freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had to go to the ER because the previous infection from 01/14/21 came roarng back. I now have pylonephritis, all which started after the 2nd pfizer dose

WBC count to 28,000. Prostatitis appears to be reducing. Body aches and fatigue are becoming milder. Mostly just tired all the time. Allergic reaction to antibiotics caused severe outbreak of hives over my body.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Coincidence or not,  i developed prostitis, severe case
Same exact time as symptoms appeared,  2 days frequent by difficult urination. Diagnosed with prostatitis
